18 February 2021 Magpies Waitara 11-37 Alexandria Parade , Waitara
Are you new to insulin, or have been on insulin for a while and would like a
refresher? This workshop provides you with key information to help you
understand insulin, the different products and equipment available, and the
importance of looking after your blood glucose levels. At the end of this
session you will leave with practical tips and tools that will support you to
feel more comfortable and confident in caring for your diabetes.
During this 3 hour session, you will learn about:
* What insulin does in your body and why you need it
